{
  "name": "Sinking Blow",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/athletics.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>If you are flying or swimming, whenever you make a successful attack action against a creature employing the same movement mode as you while you have martial focus, that creature must succeed at a Reflex saving throw or lose 30 feet of distance to the ground. If you have 10 or more ranks in the used movement mode, a creature who fails this saving throw also has their speed for that movement mode reduced by 1/2 for a number of rounds equal to your practitioner modifier (minimum 1).</p>\n",
